## ⭐ 皮肤科

picture_counter_2 A sleek, modern kitchen features matte-black cabinetry and a large white marble island with waterfall edges. Three minimalist black pendant lights hang above the island, which is paired with three backless, light-wood bar stools. Behind the island, a full-height backsplash of white marble with subtle gray veining complements the countertop. Integrated appliances and handle-less cabinets maintain a clean, uncluttered look, while warm under-cabinet lighting adds a soft glow to the space.

位置： 楼西区 2

- 路线：门诊大厅乘 1 号电梯至 2 楼，出电梯右转第一间诊室


## 科室简介

皮肤科为医院重点建设科室之一，拥有完善的诊疗体系与专业设备，长期承担区域医疗服务任务。


